window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Threadbare has reunited with his little girl, even if it didn't go exactly like he'd hoped it would.</p> <p>But war still rages through the kingdom, and the fluffy heroes must stop the tyrant king and restore peace to their home. Celia, Threadbare, and the rest of their allies must join the final resistance, to fight for the fate of everyone within Cylvania.</p> <p>It's a daunting task. Fortunately, they're not alone. Doom comes for the tyrant king, on soft, fuzzy little feet....</p> <p>The epic conclusion to the new litrpg saga!</p> <p><i>Warning: Contains profanity and violence.</i></p>"; 
